    "ideation": "The bellhop bell animation focuses on the mechanical tension and the sharp, resonant 'ding.' The eyes and mouth act as the plunger and the shell. We start in a shiny, brassy standby state. The acting arc is: a sharp downward compression (the press), a moment of held kinetic energy, the violent strike/release (the ring), and a long, shimmering decay of sound. The mouth represents the sound wave: starting flat, then exploding into a high-frequency, high-amplitude shimmer that slowly settles as the vibration dies out. Colors shift from muted brass to a brilliant, glowing gold during the peak of the ring.",
